import { IonInput, IonItem, IonLabel } from "@ionic/react"
import { Button, Col, Container, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap"
import Title from "../../components/Title"
import FormLogin from "../Login/components/FormLogin"

const NuevoUsuario: React.FC = () => { 

    return <Container>
        <Title name='Crear nuevo usuario' />
        <Form>
            <Row sm='12'>
                <Col sm='6'>
                    <FormLogin
                        title='Nombre(s)'
                        required={true}
                        minLength={4}
                        type='text'
                        name='nombre'
                        placeholder='Nombre(s)...'
                        // size="sm"
                    />
                </Col>
                <Col sm='6'>
                    <FormLogin
                        title='Apeido Paterno'
                        required={true}
                        minLength={4}
                        type='text'
                        name='apP'
                        placeholder='Apeido paterno'
                        // size="sm"
                    />
                </Col>
                <Col sm='6'>
                    <FormLogin
                        title='Apeido materno'
                        type='text'
                        name='apM'
                        placeholder='Apeido materno '
                        // size="sm"
                    />
                </Col>

                <Col sm='6'>
                    <FormLogin
                        title='Correo'
                        required={true}
                        minLength={8}
                        type='email'
                        name='user'
                        placeholder='usuario@dominio.abc'
                        // size="sm"
                    />
                </Col>
                <Col sm='3'>
                    <Button block type='submit'> GUARDAR</Button>
                </Col>
            </Row>
            
        </Form>
    </Container>
} 

export default NuevoUsuario;
